code: /**  * Extract URI template variables from the matching pattern as defined in  * {@link PathMatcher#extractUriTemplateVariables}.  * @return a map with URI template variables  */ public Map<String, String> extractUriTemplateVariables() {     return this.pathMatcher.extractUriTemplateVariables(this.matchingPattern, this.lookupPath). }
